## ✅ Quick Test Checklist (Run Top to Bottom)

```powershell
# 1. Is the server alive?
Invoke-RestMethod http://localhost:8080/

# 2. Is AD reachable (dry run)?
Invoke-RestMethod http://localhost:8080/api/ad/status

# 3. Is Gemini configured?
Invoke-RestMethod http://localhost:8080/api/ai/health

# 4. Get list of OUs (mock in dry run)
Invoke-RestMethod http://localhost:8080/api/ad/ous

# 5. Full user create flow (dry run - SAFE)
$user = '{"first_name":"Test","last_name":"User","password":"Test@1234","ou_path":"OU=IT,DC=company,DC=com"}'
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/users/validate -Method POST -ContentType "application/json" -Body $user
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/users/analyze  -Method POST -ContentType "application/json" -Body $user
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/users/create   -Method POST -ContentType "application/json" -Body $user
```

