## Request Schema Reference

### [UserCreateRequest](file:///c:/Users/WINDOWS%2010%20PRO/Documents/ActiveDirectory/Backend/user_modules.py#16-75) (used by validate, analyze, create)

| Field | Required | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `first_name` | ✅ | string | Letters/spaces/hyphens only |
| `last_name` | ✅ | string | Letters/spaces/hyphens only |
| `password` | ✅ | string | Must meet password policy |
| `ou_path` | ✅ | string | e.g. `OU=IT,DC=company,DC=com` |
| [username](file:///c:/Users/WINDOWS%2010%20PRO/Documents/ActiveDirectory/Backend/user_modules.py#63-75) | ❌ | string | Auto-generated if omitted |
| `display_name` | ❌ | string | Auto-generated if omitted |
| `user_principal_name` | ❌ | string | Auto-generated if omitted |
| `email` | ❌ | string | Valid email format |
| `department` | ❌ | string | |
| `job_title` | ❌ | string | |
| `phone` | ❌ | string | |
| `mobile` | ❌ | string | |
| `company` | ❌ | string | |
| `employee_id` | ❌ | string | |
| `manager_dn` | ❌ | string | Full DN of manager |
| `description` | ❌ | string | |
| `account_status` | ❌ | `enabled`/`disabled` | Default: `enabled` |
| `must_change_password` | ❌ | boolean | Default: `true` |
| `password_never_expires` | ❌ | boolean | Default: `false` |

### Password Policy (from [.env](file:///c:/Users/WINDOWS%2010%20PRO/Documents/ActiveDirectory/Backend/.env))
- Min 8 characters
- Requires uppercase, lowercase, number, special character
- Special characters: `!@#$%^&*(),.?":{}|<>`
